o%20having%20kids%20with%20someone%20who%20isn't%20your%20spouse.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20friends%20all%20say%20my%20only%20options%20are%20to%20accept%20his%20decision%20or%20to%20break%20up%20with%20him%20and%20find%20someone%20else.%20They're%20probably%20right%2C%20but%20I'm%20hoping%20there's%20a%20third%20way.%20Any%20ideas%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlip%20flopper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Flip%20flopper%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we're%20being%20literal%2C%20your%20friends%20are%20right.%20You%20only%20have%20two%20choices%3A%20stay%20or%20leave.%20That%20said%2C%20there%20are%20assurances%2C%20questions%2C%20and%20compromises%20that%20can%20make%20these%20options%20less%20brutal%20than%20either%20a%20sweeping%20acceptance%20of%20your%20boyfriend's%20wishes%20or%20dumping%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20before%20we%20dive%20into%20what%20some%20of%20those%20options%20look%20like%2C%20you%20must%20begin%20by%20honestly%20charting%20your%20path%20from%20being%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%26quot%3B%20OK%20with%20never%20getting%20married%20to%20where%20you%20are%20now%2C%20recognizing%20this%20may%20be%20a%20dealbreaker.%20Self-awareness%20is%20essential%20to%20making%20big%20decisions%20you%20won't%20regret%20later.%20The%20important%20thing%20is%20not%20to%20judge%20yourself%20in%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYour%20actions%20and%20words%20are%20misaligned%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20high-stakes%20choices%20like%20getting%20married%2C%20starting%20a%20family%2C%20changing%20your%20mind%2C%20or%20hoping%20your%20boyfriend%20would%20change%20his%20mind%2C%20it's%20only%20fair%20to%20recognize%20the%20social%20pressure%20just%20to%20%3Cem%3Ebe%20cool.%20%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20all%20feel%20this%20pressure%2C%20and%20when%20we%20do%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20pretend%20even%20to%20ourselves%20that%20we%20feel%20the%20way%20we%20think%20others%20expect%20us%20to%20feel%20rather%20than%20honoring%20our%20actual%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20therapist%20calls%20this%20behavior%20%26quot%3Bmisalignment.%26quot%3B%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20who%20you%20are%20on%20the%20inside%20is%20aligned%20with%20how%20you%20represent%20yourself%20on%20the%20outside.%20Sometimes%2C%20this%20means%20getting%20real%20with%20ourselves%20and%20other%20people%20about%20the%20parts%20of%20us%20that%20feel%20a%20bit%20embarrassing.%20For%20instance%2C%20admitting%20we%20desire%20old-fashioned%2C%20traditional%20ideals%20like%20marriage%2C%20even%20when%20the%20concept%20grows%20more%20pass%C3%A9%20each%20year.%20Or%2C%20admitting%20even%20less%20flattering%20truths%2C%20like%20formerly%20believing%20we%20could%20change%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20man%20who%20was%20always%20abundantly%20clear%20about%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20your%20boyfriend%2C%20as%20painful%20as%20it%20may%20be%20to%20admit%20you%20want%20different%20things%2C%20you%20have%20to%20respect%20his%20alignment.%20He%20demonstrated%20unwavering%20loyalty%20to%20his%20most%20authentic%20self%2C%20and%20your%20best%20bet%20is%20to%20follow%20his%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECompromise%20is%20still%20on%20the%20table%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20sound%20like%20I'm%20suggesting%20that%20you%20two%20break%20up.%20After%20all%2C%20if%20your%20authentic%20self%20wants%20to%20get%20married%20and%20his%20authentic%20self%20doesn't%2C%20what%20other%20options%20do%20you%20have%3F%20But%20loyalty%20to%20self%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20must%20be%20self-serving%20and%20inflexible.%20Instead%2C%20you%20can%20use%20self-awareness%20as%20a%20starting%20point%20in%20your%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20want%20lots%20of%20things%20to%20varying%20degrees%2C%20and%20determining%20what%20to%20compromise%20and%20what%20to%20keep%20becomes%20a%20matter%20of%20priorities.%20You%20may%20find%20that%20you%20and%20your%20boyfriend%20share%20the%20highest%20priority%3A%20each%20other.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20finding%20a%20compromise%20that%20will%20address%20your%20financial%20concerns%20as%20well%20as%20your%20boyfriend's%20emotional%20considerations%20is%20more%20than%20doable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20negotiate%20this%20compromise%2C%20remember%20that%20neither%20of%20you%20is%20wrong%20for%20wanting%20different%20things.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20fight%20with%20a%20win%2Flose%20outcome%20but%20a%20collaboration%20that%20will%20leave%20both%20of%20you%20feeling%20like%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonesty%20must%20be%20the%20framework%20of%20this%20conversation.%20Tell%20your%20boyfriend%20why%20marriage%20is%20important%20to%20you.%20You've%20likely%20pointed%20out%20the%20financial%20incentives%20to%20marriage%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20explain%20the%20peace%20of%20mind%20those%20financial%20incentives%20will%20give%20you%20and%20why%20you%20feel%20you%20need%20it.%20In%20turn%2C%20encourage%20him%20to%20articulate%20his%20feelings%20about%20marriage%20and%20why.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20both%20laid%20this%20foundation%20of%20honest%20vulnerability%2C%20you%20can%20build%20your%20compromise.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you're%20worried%20about%20having%20kids%20with%20him%20only%20to%20end%20up%20as%20a%20single%20parent%20should%20he%20leave%20you%2C%20you%20could%20ask%20your%20boyfriend%20for%20a%20financial%20commitment%20upfront%20to%20ease%20the%20insecurity%20of%20a%20no-legal-strings-attached%20relationship%20status.%20Perhaps%20he%20could%20set%20up%20a%20trust%20in%20your%20name%20where%20he%20compensates%20you%20for%20the%20years%20you%20are%20entrusting%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20if%20his%20marriage%20issues%20come%20down%20to%20the%20ugly%20details%20of%20his%20parents'%20divorce%2C%20perhaps%20he%20will%20feel%20more%20comfortable%20marrying%20you%20with%20a%20prenuptial%20agreement%20in%20place%20that%20legally%20protects%20him%20from%20the%20aspects%20of%20a%20potential%20divorce%20that%20worry%20him%20the%20most.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20compromise%20might%20be%20for%20you%20to%20set%20up%20your%20finances%20in%20a%20way%20that%20benefits%20one%20another%2C%20even%20without%20a%20marriage%20certificate.%20You%20can%20name%20one%20another%20as%20beneficiaries%20on%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Or%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20state%20and%20how%20long%20you've%20lived%20together%2C%20you%20could%20look%20into%20filing%20your%20taxes%20jointly%20as%20a%20common-law%20couple.%20If%20you%20are%20planning%20on%20making%20any%20big%20purchases%20in%20the%20immediate%20future%2C%20such%20as%20a%20vehicle%20or%20a%20house%2C%20get%20both%20of%20your%20names%20on%20the%20title%20to%20ensure%20your%20financial%20interests%20are%20protected%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20breakup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20options%2C%20but%20they%20all%20require%20honesty%20and%20flexibility.%20Trust%20one%20another%20with%20these%20vulnerabilities%2C%20and%20several%20%26quot%3Bthird%20ways%26quot%3B%20will%20reveal%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20close%20my%20advice%2C%20as%20a%20wife%20of%2014%20years%20and%20a%20baby%20mama%20of%2013%2C%20I%20feel%20obliged%20to%20raise%20one%20more%20point.%20Both%20of%20you%20need%20to%20ask%20yourself%20why%20sharing%20children%20seems%20like%20less%20of%20a%20commitment%20to%20you%20than%20marriage.%20The%20reality%20of%20marriage%20is%20that%20it's%20as%20permanent%20as%20Sharpie%20on%20a%20whiteboard%20%E2%80%94%20finding%20rubbing%20alcohol%20may%20be%20a%20hassle%2C%20but%20it%20will%20wipe%20right%20off%20once%20you%20do.%20Sharing%20a%20child%2C%20however%2C%20is%20as%20permanent%20as%20a%20whole%20human%20life.%20Thus%2C%20it%20should%20only%20happen%20if%20you're%20100%25%20sure%20this%20is%20something%20you%20will%20do%20well%20together%2C%20come%20what%20may%2C%20forever.%20Because%20ultimately%2C%20that's%20what%20it's%20going%20to%20take.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid