A0According%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20drank%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20Juhu%20last%20night.%20On%20his%20way%20home%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20driver%20to%20take%20him%20a%20long%20drive.%20The%20car%20came%20to%20Worli%20and%20then%20Mihir%20insisted%20that%20he%20would%20drive.%20Soon%20after%20he%20took%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20speeding%20BMW%20hit%20a%20scooter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20scooter%20were%20Kaveri%20Nakva%20and%20her%20husband%20Pradik%20Nakva%2C%20residents%20of%20Worli's%20Koliwada%20area.%20The%20fish-seller%20couple%20went%20to%20Sassoon%20Dock%20daily%20to%20fetch%20fish.%20They%20were%20on%20their%20way%20back%2C%20when%20the%20BMW%20crashed%20into%20their%20two-wheeler.%20The%20two%20were%20thrown%20into%20the%20air%20and%20crashed%20on%20the%20bonnet%20of%20the%20SUV.%20As%20the%20car%20kept%20speeding%2C%20Kaveri%20Nakva%20was%20run%20over.%20The%20car%20fled%20the%20spot%20and%20the%20woman%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20declared%20dead.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Pradik%2C%20suffered%20minor%20injuries.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20have%20said%C2%A0Mihir%20called%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20about%20the%20crash.%20His%20phone%20has%20been%20off%20since%20then.%20Four%20police%20teams%20are%20looking%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police's%20investigation%20has%20also%20revealed%20attempts%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20The%20car's%20windshield%20has%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20sticker%2C%20which%20has%20been%20scratched%2C%20apparently%20to%20conceal%20the%20vehicle's%20link%20with%20the%20Sena%20leader.%20One%20of%20the%20car's%20number%20plates%20was%20also%20removed%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20but%20police%20scanned%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20area%20to%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Sena%20Leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20termed%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20and%20assured%20action.%20%26quot%3BLaw%20will%20take%20its%20own%20course%2C%20everyone%20is%20equal%20before%20law.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20police%20and%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20similar%20case%20of%20drink-driving%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20dead%20in%20Pune.%20The%20minor%20accused%20in%20the%20Pune%20crash%20was%20speeding%20a%20Porsche%20car%20after%20a%20round%20of%20drinking.%20The%20teen's%20father%2C%20a%20prominent%20realtor%2C%20his%20mother%20and%20his%20grandfather%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%20for%20allegedly%20attempting%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720352820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5m17les8_bmw-hit-and-run_625x300_07_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-leader-rajesh-shah-mihir-shah-sena-leaders-drunk-son-was-driving-bmw-that-ran-over-mumbai-woman-sources-6052539%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20speeding%20BMW%20that%20hit%20a%20scooter%20in%20Mumbai's%20Worli%20this%20morning%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20woman's%20death%2C%20was%20being%20driven%20by%20the%2024-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20police%20sources%20have%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-leader-rajesh-shah-mihir-shah-sena-leaders-drunk-son-was-driving-bmw-that-ran-over-mumbai-woman-sources-6052539%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-leader-rajesh-shah-mihir-shah-sena-leaders-drunk-son-was-driving-bmw-that-ran-over-mumbai-woman-sources-6052539%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-leader-rajesh-shah-mihir-shah-sena-leaders-drunk-son-was-dri