%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamantha%20Bosley%20and%20guest%20pups%2C%20Romeo%20and%20Juliet.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Samantha%20Bosley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESamantha%20Bosley%2C%20a%20single%20mom%20in%20Arizona%2C%20needed%20an%20extra%20job%20to%20support%20herself%20and%20her%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202022%2C%20she%20started%20renting%20out%20her%20backyard%20as%20a%20private%20dog%20park%20through%20the%20app%20Sniffspot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20money%20she's%20making%20is%20helping%20her%20pay%20bills%20and%20do%20more%20activities%20with%20her%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Samantha%20Bosley%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20account%20manager%20from%20Scottsdale%2C%20Arizona%2C%20who%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-made-money-side-hustle-backyard-sniffspot-dog-park-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Erenting%20out%20her%20backyard%20on%20Sniffspot%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20since%202022.%20The%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscottsdale-arizona-millionaires-moving-what-its-like-photos-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScottsdale%2C%20Arizona%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdc-ranch-scottsdale-arizona-most-expensive-neighborhood-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20gone%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20managing%20bills%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20kids%20all%20on%20my%20own.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20keep%20scraping%20by%20or%20have%20my%20finances%20tight%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%20the%20room%20to%20take%20my%20kids%20on%20vacation%20or%20do%20fun%20stuff.