Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawyers%20are%20about%20to%20file%20what's%20known%20as%20a%20330.30%20motion%20to%20set%20aside%20the%20verdict.%20Their%20deadline%20for%20filing%20is%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20pre-sentencing%20motion.%20And%20it's%20based%20on%20a%20state%20statute%20that%20tells%20New%20York%20criminal%20trial%20judges%20that%20they%20must%20toss%20out%20a%20verdict%20if%20the%20defense%20proves%20that%20something%20happened%20in%20the%20trial%20that%20was%20so%20grievously%20wrong%2C%20it%20would%20never%20survive%20an%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22982%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20portion%20of%20New%20York's%20criminal%20procedure%20law%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20hopes%20to%20use%20to%20overturn%20his%20hush-money%20conviction.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885f9f1aace5b3ada4d432%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221286%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20hopes%20to%20use%20this%20section%20of%20New%20York%20law%20to%20overturn%20his%20hush-money%20conviction.%3Cp%3ENYS%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Law%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228cad2488-891e-43cc-a1ab-a1c6d0848d1a%5C%22%3EAnd%20here's%20where%20SCOTUS%20comes%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawyers%20have%20already%20given%20Merchan%20and%20prosecutors%20the%20broad%20outlines%20of%20what%20they%20believe%20those%20grievous%20330.30%20grounds%20for%20an%20appellate%20reversal%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20the%20same%20grounds%20they%20raised%20pre-trial%20in%20March%2C%20in%20arguing%20without%20success%20that%20the%20trial%20should%20be%20delayed%20until%20SCOTUS%20addressed%20presidential%20immunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonday's%20immunity%20opinion%20protects%20former%20presidents%20from%20having%20to%20defend%20themselves%20against%20evidence%20involving%20their%20%26quot%3Bofficial%20acts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221438%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Here%20is%20the%20section%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20presidential%20immunity%20opinion%20that%20bars%20official-act%20evidence.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66887a3f268f62ba18a7e4fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20presidential%20immunity%20opinion%20bars%20official-act%20evidence.%3Cp%3EUS%20Supreme%20Court%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawyers%20now%20say%20there%20were%20at%20least%20four%20times%20that%20the%20judge%20improperly%20let%20Manhattan%20prosecutors%20show%20official-act%20evidence%20to%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20four%20instances%20involved%20evidence%20from%202017%20and%20early%202018.%20(It%20was%20just%2011%20days%20before%20the%202016%20election%20when%20then-Trump%20attorney%20Michael%20Cohen%20fronted%20%24130%2C000%20in%20hush%20money%20to%20porn%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels.%20But%20Trump%20was%20in%20the%20White%20House%20when%20he%20falsified%20Trump%20Organization%20records%20throughout%202017%20to%20hide%20paying%20Cohen%20back.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22donald%20trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5983293276084a6b008b4b5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThen-president%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20a%20phone%20call.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FCarlos%20Barria%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a814823d-82c7-4ae2-8967-931af2b90475%5C%22%3ETrump%20says%20his%202017-18%20phone%20logs%20were%20official-act%20evidence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20is%20poised%20to%20argue%20that%20the%20hush-money%20jury%20should%20never%20have%20seen%20phone%20logs%20showing%20when%20and%20for%20how%20long%20Cohen's%20phone%20connected%20with%20phones%20used%20by%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20logs%20are%20neither%20%26quot%3Bacts%26quot%3B%20nor%20v