20months.%20Last%20month%2C%20terrorists%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20bus%20in%20which%20pilgrims%20were%20travelling.%20The%20bus%20fell%20into%20a%20gorge%20in%20Reasi%20district%20and%20nine%20people%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20Reasi%20incident%2C%20two%20armed%20terrorists%20entered%20a%20village%20and%20opened%20fire.%20Villagers%20informed%20authorities%20and%20security%20forces%20arrived.%20In%20the%20gunfight%20that%20followed%2C%20a%20CRPF%20personnel%20was%20killed%20and%20the%20terrorists%20shot%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%20five%20terrorists%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20separate%20encounters%20in%20the%20Kulgam%20district%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20encounters%20also%20left%20two%20soldiers%2C%20including%20a%20para-trooper%2C%20dead.%20The%20attack%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20is%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720332900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fihr4oapo_jk-terror-attacks_625x300_07_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-terror-attacks-lashkars-most-wanted-terrorist-behind-string-of-attacks-in-j-k-sources-6051996%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Pakistan-based%20operative%20of%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%20arm%2C%20The%20Resistance%20Front%2C%20is%20behind%20the%20latest%20spike%20in%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20in%20security%20agencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-terror-attacks-lashkars-most-wanted-terrorist-behind-string-of-attacks-in-j-k-sources-6051996%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-terror-attacks-lashkars-most-wanted-terrorist-behind-string-of-attacks-in-j-k-sources-6051996%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%2