w.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Ffpis-inject-rs-7-9k-cr-in-equities-in-jul-investment-over-rs-1-tn-in-2024-124070700123_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20this%2C%20total%20FPI%20investment%20in%20equities%20reached%20Rs%201.16%20lakh%20crore%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20data%20with%20the%20depositories%20showed%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Ffpis-inject-rs-7-9k-cr-in-equities-in-jul-investment-over-rs-1-tn-in-2024-124070700123_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Ffpis-inject-rs-7-9k-cr-in-equities-in-jul-investment-over-rs-1-tn-in-2024-124070700123_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Ffpis-inject-rs-7-9k-cr-in-equities-in-jul-investment-over-rs-1-tn-in-2024-124070700123_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain%20Introduces%20'Porn%20Passport'%20To%20Watch%20Adult%20Content%20Online.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20restrict%20the%20access%20to%20online%20pornography%20by%20minors%2C%20Spain%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20new%20mobile%20application%20that%20will%20not%20only%20require%20users%20to%20verify%20their%20age%2C%20but%20also%20limits%20the%20number%20of%20credits%20for%20viewing%20adult%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20Dale%20Una%20Vuelta%2C%20an%20anti-pornography%20group%20that%20campaigns%20for%20tighter%20regulations%20on%20access%20to%20adult%20content%20online%2C%20earlier%20released%20statistics%20that%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20alarming%20spread%20of%20adult%20content%20among%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20data%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%2C%26quot%3B%20Spanish%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20told%20El%20Pais%20newspaper%2C%20%26quot%3BAlmost%20half%20of%20young%20people%20under%2015%20years%20of%20age%20consume%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20will%20the%20app%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mobile%20application%2C%20officially%20called%20the%20Digital%20Wallet%20Beta%20(Cartera%20Digital%20Beta)%2C%20and%20locally%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bpajaporte%26quot%3B%2C%20will%20allow%20platforms%20to%20check%20whether%20the%20user%20is%20above%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20or%20not.%20To%20verify%20their%20age%2C%20the%20viewers%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20use%20the%20mobile%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20will%20work%20as%20a%20mobile%20phone%20wallet%20and%20will%20verify%20users'%20age%20through%20one%20of%20the%20five%20government-issued%20IDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20verified%2C%20the%20users%20will%20then%20receive%2030%20%26quot%3Bporn%20credits%26quot%3B%20with%20one-month%20validity.%20These%20credits%20will%20grant%20them%20access%20to%20adult%20content.%20Further%2C%20users%20will%20be%20able%20to%20put%20a%20request%20for%20extra%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ELaunch%20date%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mobile%20application%20will%20be%20available%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summer%2C%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20is%20being%20criticised%20by%20a%20section%20of%20activists%20and%20experts%20for%20its%20complexity%2C%20the%20Spanish%20government%20has%20defended%20the%20move.%20According%20to%20the%20government%2C%20the%20credit-based%20model%20is%20more%20privacy-friendly%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20online%20activities%20are%20not%20easily%20traceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20voluntary%2C%20as%20online%20platforms%20can%20rely%20on%20other%20age-verification%20methods%20available%20to%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20inappropriate%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20app%20is%20part%20of%20the%20broader%20effort%20to%20align%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20law%20that%20comes%20into%20effect%20in%20October%202027.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20porn%20passport%2