%C2%A0keeping%20a%20stag%20beetle%20can%20make%20you%20rich%20overnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThese%20insects%20represent%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20saproxylic%20assemblage%20in%20forest%20ecosystems%20and%20are%20noted%20for%20their%20enlarged%20mandibles%20and%20male%20polymorphism%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20recent%20study%20in%20the%20Scientific%20Data%20journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELife%20span%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%20London-based%20Natural%20History%20Museum%2C%20these%20insects%20weigh%20between%202-6%20grams%20and%20have%20an%20average%20lifespan%20of%203-7%20years.%20While%20the%20males%20are%2035-75mm%20long%2C%20the%20females%20are%2030-50mm%20in%20length.%20They%20are%20also%20used%20for%20medicinal%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20stag%20beetle%20has%20been%20derived%20from%20the%20distinctive%20mandibles%20that%20are%20found%20on%20the%20male%20ones%2C%20resembling%20an%20antler%20of%20stags.%20The%20male%20stag%20beetles%20use%20their%20distinctive%2C%20antler-like%20jaws%20to%20battle%20each%20other%20for%20the%20chance%20to%20mate%20with%20females%20during%20the%20breeding%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20can%20they%20be%20found%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EStag%20beetles%20thrive%20in%20warm%2C%20tropical%20environments%20and%20are%20sensitive%20to%20cold%20temperatures.%20They%20naturally%20inhabit%20woodlands%2C%20but%20can%20also%20be%20found%20in%20hedgerows%2C%20traditional%20orchards%2C%20and%20urban%20areas%20like%20parks%20and%20gardens%2C%20where%20dead%20wood%20is%20abundant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20they%20eat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAdult%20stag%20beetles%20primarily%20feed%20on%20sweet%20liquids%20like%20tree%20sap%20and%20the%20juice%20from%20rotting%20fruit.%20They%20mainly%20rely%20on%20the%20energy%20reserves%20they%20accumulated%20during%20their%20larval%20stage%2C%20which%20sustains%20them%20throughout%20their%20adult%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20larvae%20of%20stag%20beetles%20feed%20on%20dead%20wood%2C%20using%20their%20sharp%20jaws%20to%20scrape%20and%20extract%20splinters%20from%20the%20fibrous%20surface.%20Since%20they%20exclusively%20feed%20on%20dead%20wood%2C%20stag%20beetles%20do%20not%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20living%20trees%20or%20shrubs%2C%20making%20them%20harmless%20to%20healthy%20vegetation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720324380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fc3perj08_stag-beetle-_625x300_07_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fstag-beetle-priced-at-rs-75-lakh-each-these-beetles-are-the-worlds-costliest-insects-6047857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Did%20you%20know%20that%20an%20insect%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20Rs%2075%20lakh%3F%20The%20'stag%20beetle'%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20insects%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fstag-beetle-priced-at-rs-75-lakh-each-these-beetles-are-the-worlds-costliest-insects-6047857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fstag-beetle-priced-at-rs-75-lakh-each-these-beetles-are-the-worlds-costliest-insects-6047857%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fstag-beetle-priced-at-rs-75-lakh-each-these-beetles-are-the-worlds-costliest-insects-6047857%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starmer%20will%20get%20'fair%20hearing'%20on%20changes%20to%20post-Brexit%20deal%2C%20says%20Irish%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720323660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2