3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Environment%20Education%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceeindia.org%2Ffile%2FPOULTRY-waste-mangement-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEE%3C%2Fa%3E)%20mentions%20that%20India%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20broiler%20meat-producing%20country%20after%20the%20USA%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20China%2C%20with%20over%204.6%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20annual%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupported%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20CEE%20is%20a%20national%20institute%20dedicated%20to%20enhancing%20public%20awareness%20about%20the%20environment.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpoultry%20waste%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20as%20a%20formal%20management%20does%20not%20exist%20for%20this%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20estimated%20that%20the%20generation%20of%20poultry%20waste%20is%20approximately%2020%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20just%20within%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bpoultry%20waste%5D%20is%20either%20sold%20to%20middlemen%20(for%20processing%20some%20body%20parts%20into%20fish%20feed%2C%20manure%20etc)%20or%20disposed%20of%20in%20municipal%20dumping%20sites%20without%20any%20treatment%2C%20which%20is%20against%20the%20law%20and%20is%20causing%20issues%20related%20to%20environmental%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Radhesh%20is%20able%20to%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERadhesh%20can%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhesh%20remarks%20that%20in%20a%20country%20where%20rivers%20are%20worshipped%20as%20mothers%2C%20the%20butchery%20waste%20comprising%20intestines%2C%20blood%2C%20skin%2C%20inner%20cells%2C%20and%20feathers%2C%20ends%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297496%2Framon-magsaysay-award-winner-gary-bencheghib-cleans-plastic-from-bali-indonesia-beaches%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolluting%20river%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20spreads%20communicable%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWaste%20from%20big%20bovine%20animals%20is%20used%20to%20make%20leather%2C%20pet%20foods%2C%20and%20more%2C%20whereas%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20either%20incinerated%20or%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills%20and%20water%20bodies.%20The%20incineration%20process%20releases%20huge%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20working%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20recycling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20not%20many%20are%20talking%20about%20chicken%20butchery%20waste.%20However%2C%20instead%20of%20making%20slogans%20to%20clean%20water%20bodies%2C%20we%20really%20need%20to%20work%20on%20grassroots%20to%20solve%20the%20root%20causes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20and%20paper%20from%20chicken%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20do%20his%20bit%2C%20Radhesh%20launched%20his%20company%20in%202019.%20Explaining%20its%20functioning%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20waste%20from%20slaughterhouses%20and%20then%20we%20sterilise%20and%20sanitise%20it%20in%20a%20hygienic%20way%20using%20100%20degrees%20steam%20process%20to%20kill%20the%20various%20worms%20present%20in%20the%20waste.%20Using%20our%20patented%20technology%2C%20we%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20to%20process%20the%20waste%20into%20wool-like%20fibre%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20pashmina%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChicken%20is%20a%20fowl%20and%20it%20has%20feathers%20similar%20to%20other%20birds.%20Feathers%20themselves%20are%20lightweight%20and%20using%20that%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%20This%20woollen%20fibre%20is%20soft%2C%20warm%20and%20durable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20Radhesh%20says%20he%20has%20trained%201%2C200%20tribal%20women%20of%20Rajasthan%20who%20weave%20and%20spin%20the%20waste%20into%20fibre.%20Feathers%20which%20are%20not%20good%20for%20spinning%20are%20used%20to%20make%20handmade%20paper%20or%20converted%20into%20fillers%20for%20quilts%2C%20jackets%2C%20and%20pillows.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20the%20byproduct%20of%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20converted%20into%20compost%20and%20fish%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20collecting%20waste%20from%20slaughterhouses%2C%20the%20team%20sterilises%20and%20sanitises%20it%20to%20kill%20the%20various%20worms%20present%20in%20the%20waste.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353379%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20collecting%20waste%20from%20slaughterhouses%2C%20the%20team%20sterilises%20and%20sanitises%20it%20to%20kill%20the%20various%20worms%20present%20in%20the%20waste.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20units%20are%20established%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20Pune.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20they%20sell%20the%20products%20in%20B2B%20business%2C%20generating%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20diverted%2073%20lakh%20kg%20of%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20from%20polluting%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20work%2C%20Radhesh%20has%20received%20at%20least%2025%20national%20and%20international%20level%20awards%2C%20including%20The%20German%20Design%20Award%2C%20Lexus%20Design%20Award%2C%20and%20Swachhata%20Startup%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20the%20journey%20from%20being%20a%20designer%20to%20an%20innovator%20has%20been%20extremely%20fulfilling%20for%20me.%20I%20always%20strived%20to%20do%20impact-driven%20work%20and%20received%20many%20awards%20and%20recognition%20for%20it.%20We%20are%20working%20at%20a%20small%20level%20but%20wish%20to%20expand%20this%20pan%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20anything%2C%20we%20require%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20support%20to%20further%20our%20work%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20recycling%20model%2C%20which%20will%20help%20us%20divert%20this%20waste%20at%20a%20large%20scale.%20If%20they%20can%20also%20fund%20training%20programmes%20for%20women%20workers%20and%20design%20policies%20that%20ensure%20the%20waste%20is%20not%20thrown%20in%20water%20bodies%20or%20landfills%2C%20that%20will%20help%20us%20further%20the%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Golden%20Feathers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720017502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1-1718797523.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Radhesh%20Agrahari%20runs%20Golden%20Feathers%2C%20a%20startup%20which%20converts%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20including%20feathers%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98wool-like%E2%80%99%20fibre%20and%20handmade%20paper.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355399%2Fstartup-converting-chicken-butchery-waste-into-wool-shawls-jackets-paper-manure-golden-feather-radhesh-agrahari%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20CSR%20Initiative%20Works%20For%20Equal%20Education%2C%20Helps%20Kids%20of%20Construction%20Workers%20Join%20Schools%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Meru%20International%20School%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20you%20cannot%20help%20but%20spot%20young%20children%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20living%20in%20makeshift%20houses%20with%20their%20parents%20who%20work%20there.%20While%20they%20may%20belong%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20what%20unfortunately%20remains%20common%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20be%20due%20to%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors%20ranging%20from%20frequent%20movement%20of%20the%20parents%20to%20not%20having%20a%20basic%20understanding%20or%20not%20having%20the%20appropriate%20ID%20cards.%20However%2C%20these%20reasons%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20what%20these%20children%20are%20losing%20out%20on%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20the%20right%20to%20basic%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20happens%2C%20those%20working%20in%20the%20construction%20and%20real%20estate%20industries%20are%20most%20exposed%20to%20this%20social%20problem.%20A%20senior%20employee%20at%20My%20Home%20Constructions%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20company%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20was%20disturbed%20when%20he%20saw%20these%20children%20not%20going%20to%20school.%20They%20were%20often%20left%20behind%20unattended%2C%20which%20could%20be%20extremely%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201512px)%20100vw%2C%201512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%201512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMeru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20shared%20this%20with%20Ramu%20Rao%20Jupally%2C%20the%20vice%20chairman%20of%20My%20Home%20Constructions%2C%20Ramu%20Rao%20immediately%20agreed%20to%20help%2C%20and%20the%20team%20reached%20out%20to%20Meghana%20Gorukanti%C2%A0%20Jupally%2C%20who%20runs%20Meru%20International%20School%2C%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%20How%20could%20they%20provide%20early%20childhood%20education%20in%20a%20nurturing%20and%20safe%20environment%3F%20By%20building%20a%20daycare%20centre-cum-play%20school%20called%20the%20Meru%20Aveksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Meru%20Aveksha%20centre%20was%20opened%20last%20year%20at%20an%20upcoming%20residential%20project%20by%20the%20My%20Home%20Group%20in%20Kokapet%2C%20Hyderabad.%20Over%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20two%20more%20centres%20were%20opened%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20three%20centres%20cater%20to%20over%20150%20children%2C%20from%20infants%20to%2012-year-olds%2C%20providing%20them%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20stay%20during%20the%20day%2C%20while%20empowering%20them%20with%20the%20necessary%20skill%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafety%2C%20education%20and%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meru%20Aveksha%20team%20first%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20children%20of%20the%20migrant%20labourers%20to%20understand%20the%20major%20gaps.%20They%20found%20that%20there%20was%20no%20facility%20for%20these%20children%20to%20spend%20time%20during%20the%20day%20and%20they%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20gain%20admission%20in%20government%20schools%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20identification%20documents%20like%20an%20Aadhar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20at%20Meru%20Aveksha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-500x336.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-768x517.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-150x101.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20at%20Meru%20Aveksha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20children%20would%20either%20come%20to%20the%20site%20with%20their%20parents%20or%20stay%20at%20home.%20Some%20of%20the%20older%20children%20sometimes%20also%20start%20working%20very%20early.%20We%20wanted%20to%20provide%20them%20safety%2C%20education%20and%20food.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20this%20would%20be%20through%20a%20daycare%20and%20playschool%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20at%20construction%20sites%2C%20these%20centres%20are%20spread%20over%20half%20an%20acre.%20They%20have%20an%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20play%20area%2C%20classrooms%2C%20audio-visual%20rooms%20and%20much%20more.%20Teachers%20from%20Meru%20International%20School%20built%20a%20basic%20to%20advanced%20curriculum%20that%20would%20focus%20on%20languages%2C%20numeracy%2C%20physical%20activity%2C%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20health%20and%20hygiene%20skills%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20age%20of%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20from%208%3A30%20am%20to%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20each%20day%20starts%20with%20circle%20time%2C%20indoor%20playtime%2C%20toilet%20breaks%20(to%20inculcate%20good%20habits)%2C%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20Math%20classes%2C%20along%20with%20audio-visual%20aids%20(music%2Fdance%2Fmovies%2Fstorytelling%2Fart)%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20was%20convincing%20the%20parents.%20Only%20after%20the%20parents%20accompanied%20the%20children%20to%20the%20centre%20daily%20did%20they%20understand%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20counsel%20the%20parents%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20early%20education.%20Our%20idea%20is%20to%20create%20a%20habit%20of%20coming%20to%20a%20structured%20space%20daily.%20After%20attending%20this%20centre%20for%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20they%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20join%20a%20mainstream%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20interventions%20which%20impressed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20education%2C%20children%20started%20attending%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20basics%20of%20early%20childhood%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20centre%20has%20a%20caretaker%20and%20two%20qualified%20staff%20members.%20The%20curriculum%20is%20designed%20to%20improve%20learning%20outcomes%20and%20bridge%20the%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20students%20first%20start%20with%20a%20common%20curriculum%2C%20which%20includes%20alphabets.%20Once%20they%20progress%2C%20they%20are%20given%20textbooks%20and%20worksheets%20for%20the%20next%20level.%20They%20are%20then%20divided%20into%20smaller%20cohorts%20and%20taught%20as%20per%20their%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana%2C%20adding%20that%20each%20student%20is%20provided%20with%20a%20uniform%2C%20textbooks%20and%20worksheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Features%20of%20the%20curriculum%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355457%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20that%20the%20Meru%20Aveksha%20centre%20members%20have%20noticed%20in%20the%20children%20is%20a%20behavioural%20change.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20attitude%20towards%20themselves%20has%20changed.%20From%20not%20attending%20classes%20post-lunch%2C%20they%20all%20come%20back%20now.%20They%20have%20started%20enjoying%20themselves.%20The%20most%20critical%20change%20we%20have%20seen%20is%20that%20they%20are%20engaged%20and%20interested%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20learning%20levels%20and%20understanding%2C%20their%20socio-emotional%20skills%20have%20developed%20to%20a%20great%20extent%2C%20according%20to%20her.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20catering%20to%20a%20segment%20that%20is%20completely%20neglected.%20They%20are%20learning%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20a%20safe%20environment%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20impact%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meru%20Aveshka%20team%20wants%20to%20share%20this%20model%20with%20other%20real%20estate%20developers%20so%20that%20all%20construction%20sites%20can%20start%20a%20daycare%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20learning%20more%20about%20this%20model%2C%20you%20can%20email%20them%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ameruaveksha%40meruinternationalschool.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emeruaveksha%40meruinternationalschool.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20prevent%20children%20being%20left%20alone%20at%20home.%20Every%20child%20deserves%20a%20good%20education%20and%20a%20chance%20at%20a%20better%20life.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20give%20them%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720016654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghana%20Gorukanti%20Jupally%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Meru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha%2C%20which%20helps%20integrate%20kids%20of%20migrant%20workers%20into%20mainstream%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355387%2Fmeru-international-school-tellapur-hyderabad-migrant-workers-children-daycare-learning-centre%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Back%20To%20My%20Childhood%E2%80%99%3A%20Kerala%20Man%20Turned%20a%20Barren%20Mining%20Site%20Into%20a%20Forest%20With%20Mud%20Homestays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Mustafa%20P%20A%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20which%20is%20not%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20cup%20of%20tea.%20He%20purchased%20a%20barren%20land%20which%20was%20once%20a%20mining%20site%20to%20transform%20it%20into%20a%20green%20oasis%20with%20trees%2C%20tropical%20forests%20and%20water%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20businessman%20by%20profession%2C%20it%20was%20his%20work%20trips%20to%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20Thailand%20that%20contributed%20to%20his%20inspiration%20to%20make%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251997%2Fbengaluru-engineer-terrace-gardening-urban-jungle-organic-food-compost-green-hero-him16%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20private%20jungle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20looked%20for%20the%20perfect%20land%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20before%20finding%20this%20one.%20His%20vision%20is%20a%20lush%20green%20tropical%20forest%20today.%20The%20Greenara%20Homestay%20is%20a%20part%20of%20that%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haneena%20P%20A%2C%20his%20daughter%20who%20manages%20the%20homestay%20with%20him%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20amidst%20the%20tropical%20forest%20that%20Mustafa%20planted%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Karipur%2C%20surrounding%20it%20with%20seven%20water%20bodies%2C%20the%20homestay%20is%20the%20natural%20getaway%20of%20your%20dreams.%20The%20property%20with%20three%20stay%20options%20is%20made%20with%20natural%20materials%20like%20mud%2C%20straw%20and%20wood%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289271%2Fkerala-couple-build-zero-cement-eco-friendly-home-with-recycled-material-around-natural-rocks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20zero%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20back%20to%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20Mustafa%20always%20missed%20living%20in%20the%20lush%2C%20green%20area.%20The%20inspiration%20behind%20the%20project%20was%20partly%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20relive%20his%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20development%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Kerala%2C%20he%20felt%20like%20the%20green%20cover%20was%20reducing%20massively.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20his%20part%20in%20bringing%20it%20back%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20undertake%20the%20project.%20It%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20alerted%20him%20of%20the%20land%20where%20Greenara%20now%20stands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mustafa%20PA%2C%20founder%20of%20Greenara%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-