0says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2021%20months%20of%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20the%20mussels%20to%20turn%20into%20pearls%2C%20Gaurav%20finally%20got%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%9COur%20happiness%20knew%20no%20bounds.%20We%20fetched%20Rs%20110%20per%20pearl%20and%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crore%20and%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2080%20lakh.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20this%20profit%20in%20a%201.5%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20land%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20us.%20Farmers%20in%20200%20villages%20collectively%20could%20not%20earn%20this%20much%20by%20growing%20wheat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20I%20earned%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20after%20investing%20Rs%2021%20lakh.%20This%20was%202.5%20times%20earnings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20beams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20was%20not%20as%20easy.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20challenges%20in%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20is%20managing%20weather%20conditions.%20Rajasthan%20has%20very%20warm%20weather%20and%20it%20took%20two%20days%20of%20travel%20by%20train%20to%20source%20mussels%20from%20Odisha.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20the%20mussels%20became%20very%20weak%20as%20they%20were%20without%20water%20for%20so%20long%2C%20which%20increased%20the%20mortality%20rate%20to%2050%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20pearl%20farming%20in%20the%20extreme%20winters%20of%20January%20instead%20of%20September%20and%20October%20when%20the%20weather%20is%20still%20hot%20in%20Rajasthan.%20In%20early%202023%2C%20when%20I%20procured%20mussels%2C%20the%20mortality%20rate%20was%20just%2030%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20along%20with%20other%20farmers%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurav%20along%20with%20other%20farmers%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%20over%201.25%20crore.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20how%20many%20books%20I%20read%20or%20videos%20I%20watched%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20not%20learn%20anything%20unless%20I%20experimented%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20understood%20the%20challenges%20and%20then%20worked%20on%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20for%20the%20results%20of%20the%20first%20batch%2C%20Gaurav%20also%20started%20working%20on%20the%20second%20batch%20simultaneously%20and%20established%20another%20pond.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20interrupted%20and%20taunted%20me%20for%20this%20decision.%20They%20asked%20why%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20invest%20and%20potentially%20waste%20more%20money%20even%20before%20receiving%20any%20income%20from%20the%20first%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20takes%20around%2021%20months%20to%20prepare%20one%20batch%2C%20which%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process.%20So%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20be%20patient%20and%20hopeful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20replied%20back%20to%20any%20taunts%20but%20patiently%20waited%20for%20the%20results.%20And%2021%20months%20later%2C%20we%20earned%20Rs%201.25%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20Today%2C%20Gaurav%20has%20expanded%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20in%20three%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342922%2Fhow-to-do-pearl-farming-in-artificial-ponds-in-rajasthan-computer-teacher-reaps-huge-profits%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eponds%20in%20Rajasthan%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20two%20ponds%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20for%20myself%20but%20this%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20establish%20an%20identity%20by%20doing%20unique%20work.%20Besides%2C%20this%20work%20has%20become%20an%20income%20source%20for%20other%20small%20farmers%20who%20invested%20in%20this%20project.%20It%20was%20better%20than%20investing%20in%20mutual%20funds%20or%20fixed%20deposits.%20It%20was%20so%20fulfilling%20to%20see%20the%20results%20because%20it%20shaped%20my%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Gaurav%20Pachauri.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719845248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaurav%20Pachauri%20took%20up%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20after%20failing%20to%20crack%20government%20exams%20for%20four%20years.%20He%20set%20up%20a%20pearl%20farm%20in%20Bharatpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20earning%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20within%2021%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355072%2Ffreshwater-pearl-farming-help-local-farmers-earn-lakhs-gaurav-pachauri-bharatpur-rajasthan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%