.com%2F237813%2Fkolkata-nilanjana-chatterjee-saves-woman-molestation-abuse-hero-brave-inspiring-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20accident%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20left%20their%20daughter%20with%20multiple%20injuries%20that%20extended%20to%20her%20upper%20limbs%2C%20lower%20limbs%2C%20chest%20and%20head.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20on%20paper%20spanned%2020%20days%20in%20the%20ICU%2C%20six%20months%20in%20post-operative%20care%20along%20with%20two%20years%20of%20intensive%20physiotherapy%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20family%20is%20still%20recuperating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1719488223.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sakshi%20Maheshwari%2C%20an%20orthopaedic%20surgeon%20with%20her%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1719488223.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1719488223-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1719488223-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1719488223-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1719488223-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sakshi%20Maheshwari%2C%20an%20orthopaedic%20surgeon%20with%20her%20family%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sakshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20hit%20rock%20bottom%20the%20only%20way%20is%20up%2C%20suggests%20a%20popular%20adage.%20And%20the%20month