-based%20products%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Engandiyur%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Sumila%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20aspiration%20was%20to%20become%20a%20doctor.%20However%2C%20after%20graduating%20in%20zoology%2C%20she%20studied%20English%20Literature%20and%20was%20married%20before%20the%20results%20were%20even%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20marriage%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20with%20her%20husband.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%2C%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20twins%2C%20becoming%20an%20extremely%20occupied%20homemaker%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20six%20years%2C%20we%20shifted%20to%20Kerala%20when%20my%20husband%20went%20to%20Dubai%20for%20a%20job.%20My%20kids%20also%20moved%20out%20for%20studies.%20I%20had%20enough%20time%20on%20my%20hands%20and%20wanted%20to%20engage%20myself%20in%20work.%20I%20felt%20this%20was%20the%20right%20time%20when%20I%20could%20establish%20an%20identity%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20Sumila%20joined%20a%20local%20company%20manufacturing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307848%2Fpurvina-virgin-coconut-oil-business-by-kerala-mother-daughter-duo-ventha-velichennal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evirgin%20coconut%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20many%20queries%20about%20the%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%20and%20was%20also%20the%20one%20at%20work%20attending%20to%20all%20the%20international%20customer%20calls.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20successfully%20ensure%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20first%20export%20order%20to%20London.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-1-1719576022.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20he